óŸKarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/book/installation.mdŸ@3d691bcb08b4e8cc3d31766f6f3a93da8d2556d8af4cfe6f0bc901bf5ecf3f7a•next:ë≤Pre-built BinariesŸÿNu binaries are published for Linux, macOS, and Windows 
